      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Here, we are using a 10\xD7 magnification lens because 5\xD7 provides
        very low magnification, making the components of the slide difficult to see
        clearly, while 20\xD7 offers very high magnification, causing the components
        to appear overly focused. In this case, only a broad view is required."
